1. Get all music files
2. If necessary, get all image files
3. If necessary, get all cue files/log files
4. Move sound files into temp directory (if normalization enabled)
5. For each directory:
    1. Normalize/convert the file (if necessary)
    2. Check musicbrainz (if necessary)
    3. Apply album art (if necessary)
    4. Update cue file
    5. Move back or to new place

+ Legit installation
+ Easy console use (just 'soundboy xyz xyz')
+ Man page
+ mpd integration
+ album art
+ conversion
+ mp3 player management
+ mp3 support
+ config file (yaml) w/ global config
+ custom rename mask
